OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779131473
OL,3,CFormer Google executive Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cto begin tenure as BBC director-general
OL,6,FFormer Google boss Matt Brittin will
OL,7,Fhave his first day in the office as
OL,8,Fdirector-general of the BBC on Monday.
OL,10,FA former McKinsey consultant, Mr
OL,11,FBrittin worked for Google from 2007,
OL,12,Fleaving in 2025 after being the head
OL,13,Fof their EMEA region for a decade.
OL,15,FHe takes on the role during a
OL,16,Fturbulent time for the broadcaster as
OL,17,Fit grapples with a billion-dollar
OL,18,Flawsuit from US President Donald Trump
OL,19,Fand the fallout over a racial slur
OL,20,Fbeing aired during the Bafta film
OL,21,Fawards.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
