PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779131473
OL,3,CFormer Google executive Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cto begin tenure as BBC director-general
OL,6,FMr Brittin's salary will be #565,000,
OL,7,Fthe same figure as predecessor Tim
OL,8,FDavie, the Press Association
OL,9,Funderstands.
OL,11,FThe new BBC DG was selected as a
OL,12,Fmember of the British Olympic rowing
OL,13,Fteam in Seoul 1988 and won a bronze
OL,14,Fmedal at the World Rowing
OL,15,FChampionships in 1989.
OL,17,FThe Cambridge alumnus also rowed in
OL,18,Fthe 1987, 1988 and 1989 Boat Races.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
