PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779131473
OL,3,CFormer Google executive Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cto begin tenure as BBC director-general
OL,6,FHe was made a CBE in the King's New
OL,7,FYear Honours, list earlier this year,
OL,8,Ffor his services to technology and the
OL,9,Fenhancement of digital skills.
OL,11,FThe chairwoman of Parliament's
OL,12,FCulture, Media and Sport (CMS)
OL,13,Fcommittee, Dame Caroline Dinenage,
OL,14,Fsaid Mr Brittin "will have a
OL,15,Fsignificant job on his hands" in a
OL,16,F"period of turbulence".
OL,26,@vD@QOUwD@]O]xD@AOUxD@VO]
