OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779131473
OL,3,CFormer Google executive Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cto begin tenure as BBC director-general
OL,6,FDuring the tenure of Mr Davie, who had
OL,7,Fbeen in the top job at the BBC since
OL,8,F2020 before announcing his resignation
OL,9,Fin November 2025, the corporation
OL,10,Ffaced a number of controversies.
OL,12,FEditorial coverage led to a 10 billion
OL,13,Fdollar (#7.5 billion) lawsuit from Mr
OL,14,FTrump over the editing of a Panorama
OL,15,Fdocumentary which prompted Mr Davie's
OL,16,Fresignation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779131473
OL,3,CFormer Google executive Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cto begin tenure as BBC director-general
OL,6,FThe lawsuit claimed the documentary,
OL,7,Fwhich was broadcast in 2024, had given
OL,8,Fthe impression Mr Trump encouraged his
OL,9,Fsupporters to storm the Capitol
OL,10,Fbuilding in 2021 after he lost the
OL,11,F2020 presidential election to Joe
OL,12,FBiden.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
