OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779131473
OL,3,CFormer Google executive Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cto begin tenure as BBC director-general
OL,6,FMore recently, the corporation faced
OL,7,Fcriticism for allowing a racial slur
OL,8,Fto be broadcast during the Bafta Film
OL,9,FAwards which came after a previous
OL,10,Fediting incident over the summer when
OL,11,Fthe BBC continued to livestream the
OL,12,FBob Vylan Glastonbury set as they led
OL,13,Fchants of "death, death to the IDF
OL,14,F(Israel Defence Forces)".
OL,26,@uD@KOUvD@XO]
