PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779131473
OL,3,CFormer Google executive Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cto begin tenure as BBC director-general
OL,6,FMr Davie's time as the head of the
OL,7,Fcorporation also saw one of the BBC's
OL,8,Fhighest paid newsreaders, Huw Edwards,
OL,9,Fplead guilty to making indecent images
OL,10,Fof children and admit to having 41
OL,11,Fphotographs on WhatsApp, including
OL,12,Fseven of the most serious type.
OL,14,FMr Davie signed off days after Radio 2
OL,15,Fbreakfast host Scott Mills had his
OL,16,Fcontract with the broadcaster
OL,17,Fterminated after allegations about his
OL,18,F"personal conduct".
OL,26,@zD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
