PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779131473
OL,3,CFormer Google executive Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cto begin tenure as BBC director-general
OL,6,FThe DJ confirmed a police
OL,7,Finvestigation into allegations of a
OL,8,Fhistorical sexual offence in 2017 was
OL,9,Fabout him and that he was subjected to
OL,10,F"rumour and speculation" since the BBC
OL,11,Fannounced his sacking.
OL,13,FAt the time of his appointment, Mr
OL,14,FBrittin, 57, said: "Now, more than
OL,15,Fever, we need a thriving BBC that
OL,16,Fworks for everyone in a complex,
OL,17,Funcertain and fast-changing world.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@XO]vD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
