PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779131473
OL,3,CFormer Google executive Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cto begin tenure as BBC director-general
OL,6,F"At its best, it shows us, and the
OL,7,Fworld, who we are. It's an
OL,8,Fextraordinary, uniquely British asset,
OL,9,Fwith over 100 years of innovation in
OL,10,Fstorytelling, technology and powering
OL,11,Fcreativity. I'm honoured and excited
OL,12,Fto be asked to serve as director-
OL,13,Fgeneral."
OL,15,FHe added: "This is a moment of real
OL,16,Frisk, yet also real opportunity. The
OL,17,FBBC needs the pace and energy to be
OL,18,Fboth where stories are, and where
OL,19,Faudiences are.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@IO]wD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
