PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779131473
OL,3,CFormer Google executive Matt Brittin
OL,4,Cto begin tenure as BBC director-general
OL,6,F"To build on the reach, trust and
OL,7,Fcreative strengths today, confront
OL,8,Fchallenges with courage, and thrive as
OL,9,Fa public service fit for the future. I
OL,10,Fcan't wait to start this work."
OL,12,FMeanwhile, the BBC has published the
OL,13,Fadvert for the new deputy director-
OL,14,Fgeneral role, a role that is
OL,15,Fadvertised internally, and will close
OL,16,Fon May 25.
OL,18,FThe deputy DG will work on behalf of
OL,19,Fthe DG and will be responsible for
OL,20,Fshaping and delivering the BBC's
OL,21,Feditorial strategy and standards.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@_O]
